snippet.title: Assemble | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Assemble is a survival and horror game that supports up to 7 people with fast-paced gameplay. 

Assemble tempolu bir oynanışa sahip 7 kişiye kadar destek veren bir hayatta kalma, korku oyunudur. 

Don't forget to add to your wish list.
İstek listenize eklemeyi unutmayın.


Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1508040/Assemble
Discord : https://discord.gg/w49UrgSahQ
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/deeprangestudio/
Twitter : https://twitter.com/deeprangestudio
